title: Annihilator - Suicide Society (Deluxe Edition)  2015  320ak
description:
Suicide Society is the upcoming fifteenth album by the Canadian heavy metal band Annihilator. It is set for release on September 18, 2015 by UDR Music. The album marks a return to guitarist and bandleader Jeff Waters on lead vocals since 1997 due to the departure of vocalist and rhythm guitarist Dave Padden in December 2014. It also marks a return of bassist Cam Dixon, who was in the band from 1994 to 1995, as well as the addition of new guitarist Aaron Homma.

On this album main man Jeff Waters handles all aspects in the studio apart from the drums, played by returning stickman Mike Harshaw.

A music video for the title track was released on July 31, 2015. A lyric video for the song "Creepin' Again" was released on August 17.Another single was released, "My Revenge" in September 15, 2015.
